data.description: WOW! Pottery Barn meets Joanna Gaines's design. Many impressive features. 1st floor OFFICE not just a pocket office for your work-from-home needs. You will want to work in there all day! Big double-door ENTRY closet w/designer shelving. Gorgeous hickory-engineered wood floors on main level. FORMAL DINING & INFORMAL DINING area for all your entertaining needs. KITCHEN is so spacious & has a built-in buffet, gas stove, a big organized W/I pantry, center island w/seating, quartz cnters, tile backsplash & 2 ovens. French double doors to deck w/permanent decking overlooking the open space w/no back neighbors, fenced spacious flat backyard. 4 spacious beds on 2nd level - PRIMARY SUITE w/big W/I tiled shower w/rain heads, 2 sinks, separate H20 closet, & designer closet. All beds W/I closets & fans, J&J full bath & one private 3/4 bath. W/D, sauna, blinds, curtains, refrigerator in kitchen included in sale. Amazing lower level w/5th bed & 3/4 bath. Carriage garage doors
